Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.99,0:24:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: 変装道具
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.08,0:24:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回は旅も事件も終着！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.87,0:24:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,あの２人が出るわよ、コナンくん☆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.86,0:24:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,えぇっ
